description:
We go treasure hunting today on BEYOND the DARKNESS with an outlaw that everyone thought was dead!! Daniel J. Duke is the great great grandson of J.L. Courtney, AKA Jesse James! Dan found out from his mom that James faked his death, lived in Texas and developed a map template that would allow Duke to find ancient treasure left by secret societies all over the... UNITED STATES?! Tune in and find out the rest of the story!
